
Overview of verb clarify

The verb clarify has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (3) clarify, clear up, elucidate -- (make clear and (more) comprehensible; "clarify the mystery surrounding her death")
2. clarify -- (make clear by removing impurities or solids, as by heating; "clarify the butter"; "clarify beer")
